to calculate the costs per QWY in primary and revision THA. Preoperative QWB for 
primary THA was 0.52 ± 0.06 SD; revision was 0.53 ± 0.07 SD. The QWB change at 1 
year for primary THA was 0.08 ± 0.13 SD; revision THA was 0.06 ± 0.14 SD. 
Calculated costs per QWY were $5572 for primary procedures and $10,775 for 
revision procedures. Cost-effectiveness of THA compares favorably with other 
surgical and medical interventions such as epilepsy ablation surgery and gastric 
bypass surgery.

